questions.text:
Quyidagi kod natijasi nima bo‘ladi?
```js
const arr = [1, 2];
arr.push(3);
console.log(arr.length, arr[2]);
```

slice() qanday ishlaydi? Quyidagi chiqish qanday bo‘ladi?
```js
const a = ['a','b','c','d'];
const b = a.slice(1, 3);
console.log(a, b);
```

trim() qaysi natijani beradi?
```js
const s = '  hello  ';
const t = s.trim();
console.log('[' + t + ']', s.length, t.length);
```

join() ajratuvchi bilan birlashtirganda natija qanday?
```js
const a = [1, 2, 3];
console.log(a.join('-'));
```

pop() va indekslar:
```js
const arr = ['x','y','z'];
const p = arr.pop();
console.log(p, arr.length, arr[2]);
```

unshift() nima qaytaradi va massiv qanday bo‘ladi?
```js
const arr = [2, 3];
const n = arr.unshift(1);
console.log(n, arr[0], arr.join(','));
```

shift() qaytargan qiymat va holat:
```js
const arr = [10, 20, 30];
const f = arr.shift();
console.log(f, arr[0], arr.length);
```

split('') bilan belgilar bo‘linishi:
```js
const s = 'JS';
console.log(s.split(''));
```

slice() da manfiy indekslar:
```js
const a = [0,1,2,3,4];
console.log(a.slice(-3));
```

push() qaytargan qiymat va massiv:
```js
const arr = [1];
const r = arr.push(2);
console.log(r, arr);
```

Xatoni toping:
```js
let s = 123;
console.log(s.trim());
```

Bo‘sh massivni join qilish:
```js
const a = [];
console.log(a.join('-'));
```

pop() bo‘sh massivda:
```js
const a = [];
console.log(a.pop(), a.length);
```

unshift() bir nechta element bilan:
```js
const a = [3];
const len = a.unshift(1, 2);
console.log(len, a);
```

split() limit parametri bilan:
```js
const s = 'a,b,c';
console.log(s.split(',', 2));
```

Ichki massiv bilan join():
```js
const a = [1, [2,3]];
console.log(a.join('-'));
```

slice() start > end bo‘lsa:
```js
const a = [1,2,3,4];
console.log(a.slice(3,2));
```

trim() o‘rtadagi bo‘sh joylarga ta’sir qiladimi?
```js
const s = ' hi  there ';
console.log('[' + s.trim() + ']');
```

split(' ') da ketma-ket bo‘sh joylar:
```js
const s = 'a  b';
console.log(s.split(' '));
```

push va pop ketma-ketligi:
```js
const a = [1,2];
a.push(3);
a.pop();
a.push(4);
console.log(a.join(','));
```

slice() nusxasi va o‘zgarishlar:
```js
const a = ['x','y','z'];
const b = a.slice();
a.pop();
console.log(b.join(''), a.join(''));
```

split('') uzunligi:
```js
const s = 'hello';
console.log(s.split('').length);
```

shift() va pop() birgalikda:
```js
const a = [1,2,3,4];
const x = a.shift();
const y = a.pop();
console.log(x, y, a.join('-'));
```

join() + raqam qo‘shish:
```js
const a = [1,2,3];
console.log(a.join() + 1);
```

slice() da manfiy start va end:
```js
const a = [1,2,3,4,5];
console.log(a.slice(-4, -1));
```

Xatoni toping (split noto‘g‘ri tipda):
```js
const a = [1,2];
console.log(a.split(','));
```

trim() va split() ketma-ketligi:
```js
const s = '  a,b , c  ';
const t = s.trim().split(',');
console.log(t);
```
